Hi, and thank you for being here and for wanting to make those important swing state calls.  Our Dials from Dawn 'til Dusk are usually into swing states. Right now, we are calling Nevada.   If you go to https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1242256751445934262 and open the pinned comments at the top of that channel, there will be a link at which you can make calls any time from 9 am until midnight, EST.  If you need help, just ask in that channel and a moderator will help you.  Good luck, and thanks for the positive energy!!!
